洛杉矶办事处。负责监督资产出售的剩余员工被告知，他们的工作将于 12 月 31 日结束。 Hyperloop One 公司成立于 2014 年，通过风险投资基金和其他投资，累计筹集了大约 4.5 亿美元（约 32.13 亿元人民币）。 此前，马斯克在 2013 年提出了「alpha paper」白皮书，构想了最高时速 760 英里 / 小时的超级高铁梦想。马斯克的「超级高铁」梦，破碎了！ | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-59e82df46c143949409627cb03ad2156_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "38 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/636343940"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIlLb8hJfT25UXEAMaCTEwMzY4ODA3NyDFl5usBjAAOOwDQAlyCTYzNjM0Mzk0MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1703426806.319616", "card_id": "Q_458650020", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 159}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为啥现在的年轻人越来越多人社恐？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "年轻人社恐的根源到底是什么？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-bd98f39cf2618d894835452facfdc799_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "7 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/458650020"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IlLb8hJfT25UXEAMaCDY0MjAyNjQ5IKvC4oQGMAA4gQNACnIJNDU4NjUwMDIweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1703426806.319913", "card_id": "Q_636417072", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 106}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你认为 2023 年应该怎样结束才算完美？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-9419fd29c32e0e0e5b6ebc90065188bf_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "5.4 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/636417072"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIlLb8hJfT25UXEAMaCTEwMzcwNDM5MSCt9Z6sB